summary: 10 days till Game of Thrones season 8
body:
10 days till Game of Thrones season 8

10 expectations and speculations for season 8

1. We’re going to get lots of Jon x Dany in the first two episodes

I think we’ll get lots of J/D early on but it’ll turn tense and sour, especially after parentage reveal.

2. Death, so much death

Obviously.

3. Team Stark is going to thrive

(But Bran is probably going to die or become tree!bran saving the day)

4. Jon and Sansa!!!

This might be more of a plea but I want quality jonsa scenes which showcase their connection. I want to see them working together and quarrelling and making up and fighting and being generally awesome together and apart. I expect we’re going to get plenty of angst-filled tense scenes.

5. The Lannister’s

Will all die. Cersei’s death will be epic. Jamie’s death will be heartbreaking. Tyrion’s death is going to be just.

6. The underdogs are going to be the standouts of season 8

I’m talking Sam, Gilly, Sansa, Theon and Jamie.

7. So many fights

Whilst the fight for Winterfell might be the biggest fight, I’m expecting the “good guys” to lose the first round and to see many fights in the lead up to the fight at Kings Landing (if it happens…we all know it’s happening!)

8. Political!Jon is happening

Jon is going to listen to Sansa this time and be smart. An alliance is a political union and even if it’s not a Hans-from-Frozen moment and Jon does love Dany in some capacity, his duty to the North and the Starks will win. (I hope he isn’t in love with her though otherwise there is have no excuse for the chemistry-free season 7)


9. Cersei and Sansa will reunite

It will be epic and Cersei will die at the hands of a stark sister (although one of them may/could be wearing her brothers face)…


10. Keep one Wolf alive

Ghost and Nymeria need to make a triumphant return in season 8. It can’t just be about dragons!

It will be epic and Cersei will die at the hands of a stark sister (although one of them may/could be wearing her brothers face)…


10. Keep one Wolf alive

Ghost and Nymeria need to make a triumphant return in season 8. It can’t just be about dragons!

caption:
Til Death Do Us Part… - Life with Jon 13 (on Wattpad) https://my.w.tt/7LUrHvlwCV 

Ilva the Winter had always imagined her wedding day to be the most beautiful day of her life. And even though she loves Jon Snow more than anything else in the world, she can’t help missing the man she had planned this wedding with. But Robb Stark died on a battlefield far away from home and Ilva can only hope that he’s proud of her now. Ilva can only hope that he’s proud of her and Jon now. 

*A modern Game of Thrones fanfiction with a female OC describing the wedding day and Ilva’s life with Robb and with Jon*

summary:
Needle was Robb and Bran and Rickon, her mother and her father, even Sansa.
Needle was Winterfell's grey walls, and the laughter...
body:
Needle was Robb and Bran and Rickon, her mother and her father, even Sansa.

Needle was Winterfell’s grey walls, and the laughter of its people. Needle was the summer snows, Old Nan’s stories, the heart tree with its red leaves and scary face, the warm earthy smell of the glass gardens, the sound of the north wind rattling the shutters of her room.

Needle was Jon Snow’s smile. He used to mess my hair and call me “little sister,” she remembered, and suddenly there were tears in her eyes.

•

[Arya, A Feast For Crows]
